    <item>
      <title>白宫的米兰（Miran）拒绝衰退恐惧，吹捧放松管制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/white-house-s-miran-rejects-recession-fear-touts-deregulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫首席经济学家史蒂芬·米兰（Stephen Miran）驳斥了对华尔街经济衰退的加深恐惧，称唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的放松管制和减税计划将远远抵消关税远足的任何打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/white-house-s-miran-rejects-recession-fear-touts-deregulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 17:45:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普延长了Tiktok截止日期75天，以节省我们的应用程序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-extends-tiktok-deadline-75-days-for-deal-to-save-app-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他已决定将中国公司Bytedance Ltd.的截止日期延长，以剥离Tiktok的美国业务，并给他的政府更多时间来最终确定该国流行应用程序运行的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-extends-tiktok-deadline-75-days-for-deal-to-save-app-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 17:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织再次在阿根廷见面，因为前期付款证明了有争议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/imf-met-again-on-argentina-as-upfront-payment-proves-contentious</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，国际货币基金组织的执行委员会本周开会，讨论在华盛顿举行的非正式会议上讨论新的阿根廷计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/imf-met-again-on-argentina-as-upfront-payment-proves-contentious</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 17:15:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴菲特说，X上归因于他的评论都是错误的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/buffett-says-comments-attributed-to-him-on-x-tiktok-all-false</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔·哈瑟韦公司（Berkshire Hathaway Inc.）周五表示，所有报告在社交媒体网站上流传着X，Tiktok和Facebook在内的“关于沃伦·巴菲特（Warren Buffett）据称发表的评论”都是错误的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/buffett-says-comments-attributed-to-him-on-x-tiktok-all-false</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 16:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
