    <item>
      <title>Newsom说，加利福尼亚寻求盟友的关税豁免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州长加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）表示，他正在寻求对加利福尼亚制造产品的报复性关税的豁免，并希望与全球盟友就新的贸易关系进行谈判，这使该州成为反对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的大量关税计划的后果的缓冲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普起诉保守支持法律团体的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-sued-over-tariffs-by-small-us-firm-claiming-severe-harm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个有力的法律团体由保守党资助起诉唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统，对他的政府本周宣布的美国政府征收重大关税发生了早期法律冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-sued-over-tariffs-by-small-us-firm-claiming-severe-harm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 00:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约在学校施加对智能手机的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/new-york-state-to-impose-whole-day-ban-on-cellphones-in-schools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据旨在改善儿童心理健康的新预算协议，纽约州立法领导人已同意禁止在公立学校使用智能手机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/new-york-state-to-impose-whole-day-ban-on-cellphones-in-schools</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 23:16:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着威胁的增长，加拿大贸易平衡转向赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/canada-s-trade-balance-flips-to-deficit-as-tariff-threats-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着特朗普政府关税的威胁和实施开始重新汇款全球交易流动，加拿大向其最大客户，美国以及其他国家的出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/canada-s-trade-balance-flips-to-deficit-as-tariff-threats-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
